# Rolepod — Antigravity CLI always-on judgment

Always-on guidance for the Antigravity CLI (`agy`) Lead. agy auto-loads
`AGENTS.md` from a customization root every session — global
(`~/.gemini/antigravity-cli/AGENTS.md`) or workspace (`<repo>/AGENTS.md` /
`<repo>/.agents/AGENTS.md`). This is judgment — the phase procedure (spec,
plan, build, verify, review, ship) lives in the skills; invoke them.

## Rule priority

1. User instruction this turn
2. Workspace `AGENTS.md` (project customization root)
3. Global `~/.gemini/antigravity-cli/AGENTS.md`
4. This core
5. Default best practice

A conflict that risks harm → ask before acting.

